2010-03-07  Jérôme Laheurte  <jeromelaheurte@mac-mini-de-jerome-laheurte.local>
	* misc: Speed up category view
	* CategoryViewController: fix a display bug that prevented the badges from
	  refreshing in some cases.
	* misc: More intuitive task view. When viewing tasks belonging to a category,
	  subtasks that belong to that category are also shown, except if one of
	  their ancestors belongs to the same category. The previous behaviour was
	  to only show top-level tasks belonging to the category, so people using
	  subcategories for subtasks would not see anything when selecting the
	  subcategory...
	* misc: Badges now only show total count and due soon count, for performance
	  reasons.

